question: What is the location of the Gyeongju City Hall in Gyeongju, South Korea?
asked_question_translated: Kus asub Gyeongju linnavalitsus Gyeongjus, Lõuna-Koreas?
answer: Gyeongju linnavalitsus asub Heungmu-ro tänaval, Hwangseong-dongi piirkonnas Gyeongjus, Lõuna-Koreas.
answer_translated_eng: Gyeongju City Hall is located on Heungmu-ro Street, Hwangseong-dong District in Gyeongju, South Korea.
